		do wait(1)
		
		Disposable_worker: Ouch
		Disposable_worker: Listen buddy
		Disposable_worker: This is just plain black coffee without any of the stuff I said
		Disposable_worker: Back in my day, robots just did things
		Disposable_worker: People used to be able to press a button
